    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s build featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated double-VANOS system. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to address the chassis's inherent longitudinal stress points. Suspension is upgraded with Bilstein dampers for neutralized body roll and sharper turn-in. It retains the factory mechanical LSD for predictable power delivery. Mechanically sound with rod bearings addressed, this driver-spec M3 offers visceral performance and high-RPM induction notes.",
